=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試下都無壞嘅我諗 轉下餐單</blockquote><br />\n餓死個人咪可以殺死曬d癌細胞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"730a92d5e1b7cc91b0961c2e5d4ffd9adad8a8e8","tid":381292,"uid":1925,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T23:08:07.000Z","msg":"大麻"},{"pid":"add3620eacc0a78417ba52562e68c3797c3c890e","tid":381292,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T23:11:30.000Z","msg":"葵扇子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2fa81c2279b2700b5c667ddbb5388ee7cc3e1c7","tid":381292,"uid":130394,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T23:43:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有個 frd 生腦癌<br />\n已經末期<br />\n做過化療，食過藥都冇用<br />\n情況愈來愈差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想幫佢，所以上黎問下各位有冇啲咩成功醫好腦 cancer 嘅例子 同埋有咩特別嘅醫治方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n曬太陽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 紫外光殺撚死曬佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 或者用金寶綠水."},{"pid":"cfe08357b996f689f4ce78217f9de058a6676476","tid":381292,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T23:45:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>啲人講話戒糖戒carbohydrates <br />\n好似唔知邊度睇話癌細胞嘅營養 能量嘅來源係carbohydrates 定carbohydrates 入面嘅某種野<br />\n話只要戒左自然會餓死啲癌細胞<br />\n話科學家一早發現 想搵錢先唔講出黎<br />\n不過幾成真就唔知<br />\n我都係聽返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試下都無壞嘅我諗 轉下餐單</blockquote><br />\n餓死個人咪可以殺死曬d癌細胞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSad but true<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a09e62753daa1785461d930c8bce275a0e02848","tid":381292,"uid":48817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T00:03:41.000Z","msg":"MSM + Vitamin C treatment"},{"pid":"10ab421b582a0d34e0ce4874daed9d7d64dae216","tid":381292,"uid":48817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T00:08:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>MSM + Vitamin C treatment</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cancertutor.com/faq_msm/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cancertutor.com%2Ffaq_msm%2F&d=gswt8M6u1mfJYko8XLP10Nr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=6f7debb8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cancertutor.com/faq_msm/</a>"},{"pid":"2a56a3e000c2709aefd86c2dcc874f9c67e7e77b","tid":381292,"uid":61462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T00:19:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲人講話戒糖戒carbohydrates <br />\n好似唔知邊度睇話癌細胞嘅營養 能量嘅來源係carbohydrates 定carbohydrates 入面嘅某種野<br />\n話只要戒左自然會餓死啲癌細胞<br />\n話科學家一早發現 想搵錢先唔講出黎<br />\n不過幾成真就唔知<br />\n我都係聽返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試下都無壞嘅我諗 轉下餐單</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCancer cells have a unique physiology and prefer to get their energy from sugars. Lowering carbohydrates in the diet (starches, sugars, sweets, fruit, etc.) may be one of the reasons this works.&nbsp;It is well known that a&nbsp;low-glycemic&nbsp;load (low carb, low sugars, low sweets) diet inhibits cancer growth. A low glycemic diet is healthier for you in many ways, not only lowering cancer risk but also lowering risk of heart disease, diabetes and obesity.<br />\n<br />\ntoo good to be true<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c1a0be71b9e00202086ec82ca04227193bf561b","tid":381292,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T00:34:10.000Z","msg":"黑絲套老雞煲湯"},{"pid":"098684c53f0c0e8dad541437dc8c331dc4c796e1","tid":381292,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T01:10:21.000Z","msg":"藥用大麻，重cbd個隻<br />\n同埋用oil個隻食，唔使吸都得"},{"pid":"175f58456c8d5bda0e0f558291cd128e16cb39ce","tid":381292,"uid":20736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T08:52:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>啲人講話戒糖戒carbohydrates <br />\n好似唔知邊度睇話癌細胞嘅營養 能量嘅來源係carbohydrates 定carbohydrates 入面嘅某種野<br />\n話只要戒左自然會餓死啲癌細胞<br />\n話科學家一早發現 想搵錢先唔講出黎<br />\n不過幾成真就唔知<br />\n我都係聽返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試下都無壞嘅我諗 轉下餐單</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCancer cells have a unique physiology and prefer to get their energy from sugars. Lowering carbohydrates in the diet (starches, sugars, sweets, fruit, etc.) may be one of the reasons this works.&amp;nbsp;It is well known that a&amp;nbsp;low-glycemic&amp;nbsp;load (low carb, low sugars, low sweets) diet inhibits cancer growth. A low glycemic diet is healthier for you in many ways, not only lowering cancer risk but also lowering risk of heart disease, diabetes and obesity.<br />\n<br />\ntoo good to be true<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不過唔知有無人成功過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3b0f1645ca4748d1c9b94fc09e5eace67b2f39a","tid":381292,"uid":38098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T08:54:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://vignette4.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/9/98/The_Power_of_Masturbation.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20101231152609\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvignette4.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F9%2F98%2FThe_Power_of_Masturbation.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20101231152609&h=5b27af73&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}